CREDITS
==============================================================================

This plugin was based on and inspired by Per Liedman's Leaflet Control Geocoder
https://github.com/perliedman/leaflet-control-geocoder.

Thanks, credits and kudos go to Per for making a well structured plugin and for
making it available under an Open Source license.

Gary Gale (http://www.garygale.com/) extended it to use the OpenCage Geocoder.
